item.title: What we are vs. What we are not
item.description: ARE: An independent system parallel to - not in conflict or competition with - existing systems or institutions. ARE NOT: USATF or AAU affiliated or sanctioned organization. ARE: Sports team that exists and represents its community, city and partners year round. ARE NOT: Running group, throws camp, jumpers clinic. ARE:: First step towards a pyramid of pro, semi-pro, competitive rec teams and leagues in athletics. ARE NOT: Track meet, series or circuit; fitness games; corporate wellness; charity; science fair project.
